  * riscv: support various extensions: Zacas, Zcmp, Zfbfmin,
    Zvfbfmin, Zvfbfwma, Smcsrind/Sscsrind, XCvMem, XCvBi, XCvElw,
    XSfCease, all at version 1.0;
